<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr gnade
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie ewch
                            <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Sneid<ex>er</ex></expan> von Nappurg fürbracht hab, daz er gen uns
                        versagt und in <expan>sorge<ex>n</ex></expan> vor uns sein sülle etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu ist uns zu disen
                                <expan>zeite<ex>n</ex></expan> niht
                            <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, waran
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Sneid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns getan soll <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> welh die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das
                        antreffe, daz wir darczu niht <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
<expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan>, als ewr gnade wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> mag. Wurd uns
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> das zu wissen getan oder welh die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in in
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan>
<expan>sölte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        red <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören und ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> tun, ob das an uns
                            <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> wurd. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan> judica.</ab>
</div>
